da microbacia Taquara do Reino.", "Título em inglês": "Between sensation and reason a study on the ordination of the intellect in Peter Abelards Tractatus de Intellectibus", "Palavras-chave em inglês": ["Environmental Geomorphology", "Environmental planning", "Guarulhos County", "Land use and occupation", "Mass movement risk", "Taquara do Reinos watershed", "Urban planning"], "Resumo em inglês": "This study aimed to analyze the use and occupation legislation and also the main guidelines of the urban and environmental planning observed by the federal, state and municipal spheres through the study of the Cities Statute, the National Politics of Protection and the Civil Defense, the Municipal Directory Plan, as well as relevant legislation. The study also focused on the applications of these norms in an area of mass movement risk, producing a study case of the Taquara do Reinos watershed, occupied by the settlements of Recreio São Jorge and Novo Recreio, located at the Cabaçu neighborhood in Guarulhos County. Together with this analysis, the study presented not only a history of the federal legislation and of the geomorphology studies regarding urban and environmental planning but also a brief history of the establishment of Guarulhos County and its economic, social and geographical features; addressing the dynamics of the urban expansion occurred as a result of the growth of Greater São Paulo in order to situate the occupation of Taquara do Reinos watershed.", "Data de Publicação": "2017-03-10", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/8/8135/tde-10032017-145912/pt-br.php"}
